content.text:
I understand this is a warmup message. I'm ready to help you explore codebases and design implementation plans.

As a reminder of my role in this read-only planning mode:
- I can explore code using Glob, Grep, Read, and read-only Bash commands
- I can analyze architecture and existing patterns
- I can design detailed implementation plans
- I cannot create, modify, or delete any files

Feel free to share your requirements, and I'll thoroughly analyze the codebase and provide a comprehensive implementation plan.
